languages.text: "Поверь, Касс, ты не одна здесь чувствуешь себя последней дурой. Мои шепотки тоже предательски молчали".
"Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

languages.text: 「信じて、カシア。ここで愚か者のように感じているのはあなただけじゃないわ。私のささやき声も、裏切るように静かだった」
languages.original_text: "Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

languages.text: “说真的，小卡，觉得自己像个傻瓜一样的人，并不只有你一个。那个时候，我脑海中的耳语也莫名其妙地安静下来了。”
languages.original_text: "Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

traits.locale_text: “说真的，小卡，觉得自己像个傻瓜一样的人，并不只有你一个。那个时候，我脑海中的耳语也莫名其妙地安静下来了。”
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: «Créeme, Cass, no eres la única que se siente tonta por aquí. Mis susurros tampoco dijeron nada al respecto».
languages.original_text: "Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

traits.locale_text: «Créeme, Cass, no eres la única que se siente tonta por aquí. Mis susurros tampoco dijeron nada al respecto».
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: "Glaubt mir, Cass, ihr seid nicht die Einzige, die sich hier reichlich dumm vorkommt. Auch meine Flüsterer waren trügerisch leise."
languages.original_text: "Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

languages.text: « Croyez-moi, Cass, si je vous dis que vous n'êtes pas la seule à vous sentir complètement perdue ici. Mes murmures ont été étrangement silencieux depuis qu'on est arrivés. »
languages.original_text: "Believe me, Cass, you are not the only one feeling like a fool around here. My whispers were treacherously silent too."

languages.text: "İnan bana Cass, burada kendini aptal gibi hisseden tek kişi sen değilsin. Benim fısıltılarım da sessizliğe boğulup beni yalnız bıraktı."
